author: Nintendo of America
description:
Disney Dreamlight Valley: Wishblossom Ranch expansion launches on Nov 19, 2025 on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/disney-dreamlight-valley-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1057-01&utm_id=P1057-01  

Befriend four new Villagers and three horses from beloved Disney movies. Rebuild the ranch of your dreams, forge bonds with your horses, and help restore the Ranch to its former glory as you saddle up for a new Disney adventure!
